hopobject.body: Why did you come to ? erythromycin eth such 500mg tablets It's no surprise that the wedding between a Hollywood actress and a French luxury-goods mogul wouldn't be anything less than A-list. Though they legally wed in a small civil ceremony on Valentine's Day in 2009, Salma Hayek and Francois-Henri Pinault went for a repeat performance two months later on April 25 - only grander. Celebs like Penelope Cruz, Charlize Theron, Edward Norton and U2's Bono joined in the festivities at Venice's Teatro La Fenice.
